{"tid":1279131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家冷靜啲先 唔好咁驚網絡攻擊住","createTime":"2019-07-02T15:04:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T15:08:41.000Z","uid":59965,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8b42c7f7130dcc054856cbc004a3eed507a391a7","tid":1279131,"uid":59965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:04:25.000Z","msg":"第一<br />\n要知道所謂網絡攻擊唔係打個enter就做到嘅事 唔好聽人講咩試下先 遲下先認真打<br />\n<br />\n因為唔認真打 係冇可能打得入cloudflare<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以唔好咁緊張咁驚住 其實每日都會有ddos攻擊<br />\n咩緊要時期就會認真打 係唔成立嘅 最多叫大啲規模嘅攻擊<br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n作為一間國際級嘅網絡保安公司<br />\n其實cloudflare已經好耐冇試過down咁耐<br />\n今次打入左 之後再要入個難度又會再高左<br />\n所以其實係好安全<br />\n<br />\n只要連仔一日唔賣料 <br />\n大家都冇需要過份擔心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都明大家擔心冇左連登會點<br />\n不過只係想同大家講唔需要太恐慌<br />\n通常都唔會維持好長嘅時間 所以都唔洗太驚"},{"pid":"6c8c7212ed2458bb42c7abb969ea5effd7bfdf70","tid":1279131,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:04:47.000Z","msg":"冇擔心過"},{"pid":"210f5c330c4d2e7d50dd67818891e8ec1feb8dbb","tid":1279131,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"上唔到連登 就去登記做選民啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>今晚2359截</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://kbfl-campaign.github.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkbfl-campaign.github.io&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRc9qUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=cacbc7ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kbfl-campaign.github.io</a><br />\n直接網上填表唔洗寄3分鐘搞掂<br />\n[麻煩大家幫手share出去 7月2號就截止申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" 